Matthew KEEFE, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Xavier FERNANDEZ, et al., Defendants,
and
Borough of Ridgefield, Ridgefield Fire Department, Trustees of Ridgefield Ladder Company No. 1, Gary Chartoff, and Andrew Chartoff, Defendants-Respondents,
and
Melissa Chartoff, Defendant-Respondent. C-241 September Term 2017
079899 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 26, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003760-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
